(ns ui.components.charts
  (:require [reagent.core :as r]))

;; Simple placeholder charts that don't rely on Oz

(defn performance-chart [perf-data]
  [:div.chart-placeholder
   [:div.alert.alert-info
    [:h4 "Performance Chart"]
    [:p "This is a placeholder for the performance chart. Data is available but visualization is simplified for now."]
    [:p "Data points: " (count perf-data)]]])

(defn positions-pie-chart [positions]
  [:div.chart-placeholder
   [:div.alert.alert-info
    [:h4 "Positions Allocation"]
    [:p "This is a placeholder for the positions allocation chart."]
    [:p "Positions: " (count positions)]
    [:ul
     (for [type (distinct (map :type positions))]
       ^{:key type}
       [:li (str (clojure.string/capitalize type) ": "
                 (count (filter #(= (:type %) type) positions)) " positions")])]]])

(defn drawdown-chart [perf-data]
  [:div.chart-placeholder
   [:div.alert.alert-info
    [:h4 "Drawdown Analysis"]
    [:p "This is a placeholder for the drawdown analysis chart."]
    [:p "Data points: " (count perf-data)]]])

(defn instrument-performance-chart [instrument-data]
  [:div
   [:div.chart-placeholder
    [:div.alert.alert-info
     [:h4 "Price History"]
     [:p "This is a placeholder for the price history chart."]
     [:p "Instrument: " (:instrument instrument-data)]
     [:p "Price data points: " (count (:price-history instrument-data))]]]

   [:div.chart-placeholder.mt-3
    [:div.alert.alert-info
     [:h4 "Returns Analysis"]
     [:p "This is a placeholder for the returns analysis chart."]
     [:p "Return data points: " (count (:returns instrument-data))]]]])
